dermine%20its%20capacity%20for%20war%2C%20a%20senior%20US%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20should%20give%20China's%20leadership%20pause%20about%20how%20deep%20and%20how%20systemic%20that%20corruption%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Ely%20Ratner%2C%20US%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20defense%20for%20Indo-Pacific%20Security%20Affairs%2C%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20what%20degree%20this%20very%20advanced%20military%20is%20going%20to%20work%20when%20they%20need%2C%20and%20frankly%20are%20they%20ready%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwarontherocks.com%2F2024%2F02%2Fsecurity-in-the-indo-pacific-with-assistant-secretary-of-defense-ely-ratner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWar%20on%20the%20Rocks%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast%20host%20Ryan%20Evans%2C%20Ratner%20said%20the%20corruption%20observed%20within%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20typically%20involves%20top%20officers%20getting%20rich%20or%20people%20buying%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20graft%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20sloshing%20around%20in%20a%20very%20opaque%20system%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20lining%20their%20pockets%2C%26quot%3B%20Ratner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-punished-over-600000-officials-amid-xis-corruption-clampdown-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estamping%20out%20rampant%20government%20corruption%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20key%20pillars%20of%20his%20tenure%2C%20and%20Ratner%20assessed%20that%20this%20was%20largely%20an%20effort%20to%20restore%20order%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20down%20with%20the%20big%20banquets%2C%20down%20with%20the%20really%20expensive%20'bai%20jiu%2C'%20back%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ratner.%20%26quot%3BBai%20Jiu%26quot%3B%20is%20Chinese%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20according%20to%20Ratner%2C%20Xi's%20latest%20military%20purge%20indicated%20a%20more%20serious%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20appointments%20and%20responsibilities%20of%20those%20ousted%20indicate%20the%20purge%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20not%20only%20on%20this%20traditional%20question%20of%20graft%20but%20also%20the%20material%20effect%20on%20their%20modernization%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20Ratner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20corruption%20revealing%20itself%20not%20only%20because%20some%20general%20has%20a%20really%20fat%20bank%20account%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20but%20rather%20because%20a%20specific%20capability%20isn't%20really%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20Ratner%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20money%20that%20has%20been%20siphoned%20off%20has%20resulted%20in%20detrimental%20effects%20to%20their%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXi's%20anti-corruption%20sweep%20last%20year%20extended%20as%20high%20as%20China's%20defense%20minister%2C%20Li%20Shangfu%2C%20who%20was%20replaced%20in%20October.%20Several%20top%20commanders%20were%20also%20fired%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-rocket-force-corruption-us-cannot-lower-guard-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20Rocket%20Force%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20branch%20that%20Xi%20has%20emphasized%20as%20key%20to%20Beijing's%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-01-06%2Fus-intelligence-shows-flawed-china-missiles-led-xi-jinping-to-purge-military%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%20that%20the%20results%20of%20the%20graft%20were%20so%20serious%20they%20could%20force%20Beijing%20to%20reassess%20its%20capacity%20for%20aggression%20in%20the%20region%2C%20citing%20examples%20from%20US%20intelligence%20that%20said%20some%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-corruption-rocket-force-water-fuel-xi-ji