Comes%20Into%20Effect%3A%20Here's%20What%20To%20Know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EForeign%20tourists%20must%20now%20pay%20a%20%2410%20tax%20to%20enter%20Bali%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20tourist%20destinations.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20tourist%20tax%2C%20which%20was%20first%20announced%20last%20year%2C%20came%20into%20effect%20from%20Wednesday.%20The%20Indonesian%20government%20said%20that%20this%20move%20aims%20to%20preserve%20the%20culture%20and%20environment%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BIsland%20of%20Gods%26quot%3B.%20It%20applies%20to%20foreign%20tourists%20entering%20the%20province%20from%20abroad%20or%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20But%20domestic%20tourists%2C%20diplomatic%20visa%20holders%20and%20ASEAN%20nationals%20are%20exempted%20from%20the%20tax%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20levy%20is%20aimed%20at%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20culture%20and%20the%20environment%20in%20Bali%2C%26quot%3B%20Bali's%20acting%20governor%20Sang%20Made%20Mahendra%20Jaya%20said%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EAFP%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20applies%20to%20all%20international%20travellers%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20age%20and%20gender%2C%20including%20children.%20Tourists%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20tax%20each%20time%20they%20arrive%20in%20Bali.%20The%20fee%20will%20have%20to%20be%20paid%20electronically%20via%20the%20%26quot%3BLove%20Bali%26quot%3B%20online%20portal%20and%20will%20apply%20to%20foreign%20tourists%20entering%20Bali%20from%20abroad%20or%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20Indonesia%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68291726%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETourists%20who%20do%20not%20want%20to%20pay%20online%20can%20also%20pay%20at%20arrival%20points%2C%20such%20as%20airports%20and%20seaports%20through%20multiple%20payment%20methods%2C%20including%20credit%20cards%2C%20bank%2