C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107697946.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMalaika%20Arora%20raises%20the%20temperature%20in%20a%20black%20mini%20dress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fmalaika-arora-steals-hearts-in-a-noir-rich-black-mini-dress-with-sculpted-wing-sleeves%2Fphotostory%2F107697946.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Supreme%20Court%20Struck%20Down%20The%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%3A%205%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20which%20had%20been%20brought%20in%202018%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20cash%20donations%20made%20to%20political%20parties%20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding.%20A%20five-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20delivered%20two%20separate%20but%20unanimous%20verdicts%20on%20pleas%20challenging%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20major%20remarks%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20electoral%20bonds%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20%26quot%3BElectoral%20bonds%20scheme%20has%20to%20be%20struck%20down%20as%20unconstitutional.%20It%20violates%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20citizens%2C%20about%20possible%20quid%20pro%20quo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20%26quot%3BThe%20issuing%20bank%20shall%20forthwith%20stop%20the%20issue%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20shall%20furnish%20the%20details%20of%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20the%20details%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20which%20received%20the%20contributions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20%26quot%3BFinancial%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties%20are%20made%20for%20two%20parties%20-%20for%20support%20to%20political%20party%2C%20or%20contribution%20may%20be%20way%20of%20quid%20pro%20quo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20%26quot%3BNot%20all%20political%20contributions%20are%20made%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20alter%20public%20policy.%20Students%2C%20daily%20wagers%20etc%20also%20contribute.%20To%20not%20grant%20umbrella%20of%20privacy%20to%20political%20contributions%20only%20because%20some%20contributions%20are%20made%20for%20other%20purposes%20is%20not%20impermissible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20%26quot%3BA%20company%20has%20more%20graver%20influence%20on%20the%20political%20process%20than%20contributions%20by%20individuals.%20Contributions%20by%20companies%20are%20purely%20business%20transactions.%20Amendment%20to%20Section%20182%20Companies%20Act%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20for%20treating%20companies%20and%20individuals%20alike.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20%26quot%3BElectoral%20bonds%20scheme%20is%20not%20the%20only%20scheme%20to%20curb%20black%20money.%20There%20are%20other%20alternatives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707978540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Ftthv9vd8_supreme-court-india-generic-pti_625x300_10_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-scheme-violates-right-to-information-supreme-court-5061164%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20which%20had%20been%20brought%20in%202018%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20cash%20donations%20made%20to%20political%20parties%20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-scheme-violates-right-to-information-supreme-court-5061164%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-scheme-violates-right-to-information-supreme-court-5061164%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-scheme-violates-right-to-information-supreme-court-5061164%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%3A%20Muslim%20Groups%20Urge%20Citizens%20Not%20to%20Take%20Part%20in%20Govt%20Schools'%20Surya%20Namaskar%20Programmes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24151818%2F118281528_2076660359130829_177884413909856846_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%E2%80%99s%20directions%20to%20all%20government%20schools%20in%20the%20state%20to%20organise%20collective%20performances%20of%20the%20Surya%20Namaskar%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Surya%20Saptami%20on%20February%2015%2C%20Muslim%20organisations%20in%20the%20state%20on%20Wednesday%20have%20appealed%20to%20all%20monotheistic%20teachers%2C%20parents%20and%20students%20from%20the%20community%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20Surya%20Namaskar%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20Forum%20%E2%80%93%20an%20umbrella%20body%20representing%20various%20organisations%20including%20Jamaat%20e%20Islami%20Rajasthan%2C%20Milli%20Council%20Rajasthan%2C%20Jamiat-E-Ulema%20Rajasthan%20and%20Mansoori%20Samaj%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Sunday%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%20saying%20that%20in%20Islam%2C%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20order%20of%20the%20Quran%20to%20worship%20only%20one%20god%20(Allah)%2C%20and%20the%20act%20of%20Surya%20Namaskar%20amounts%20to%20worshipping%20the%20Sun%20God%20according%20to%20Hindu%20customs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%20according%20to%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Quran%2C%20no%20Muslim%20can%20do%20Surya%20Namaskar%2C%20worshipping%20the%20sun%20at%20any%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20Muslim%20Forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Muslim%20Forum%20issued%20the%20statement%20hours%20after%20the%20Rajasthan%20high%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20dismissed%20its%20petition%20challenging%20the%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20Secondary%20Education%20Department%2C%20Bikaner%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLearned%20Senior%20Counsel%20for%20the%20petitioners%20wants%20to%20withdraw%20this%20writ%20petition%20with%20liberty%20to%20file%20a%20fresh%20writ%20petition.%20The%20petition%20is%20dismissed%20accordingly%20with%20liberty%20as%20aforesaid%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20court%20of%20Justice%20Mahendar%20Kumar%20Goyal%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Muslim%20forum%20also%20cited%20an%20order%20of%20the%20secondary%20education%20department%20dating%20back%20to%202015%2C%20when%20it%20had%20clarified%20that%20the%20Surya%20Namaskar%20is%20part%20of%20Yoga%20and%20it%20is%20up%20to%20the%20free%20will%20of%20the%20student%20to%20decide%20which%20Yoga%20is%20to%20be%20practiced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Rajasthan%20Muslim%20Forum%2C%20which%20is%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20for%20more%20than%2020%20Muslim%20organisations%20in%20the%20state%2C%20has%20appealed%20to%20Muslim%20teachers%2C%20students%20and%20parents%20not%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Surya%20Namaskar%20event%2C%20exercising%20their%20right%20of%20religious%20independence%20as%20given%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Naeem%20Rabbani%2C%20member%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Muslim%20Forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20issued%20in%20January%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Secondary%20Education%20Department%2C%20Bikaner%20had%20directed%20all%20district%20education%20officials%20to%20hold%20practice%20sessions%20of%20the%20Surya%20Namaskar%20during%20school%20prayers%20everyday%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20February%2015%20event.%20The%20order%20added%20that%20data%20pertaining%20to%20those%20who%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20event%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98world%20record%E2%80%99%20is%20also%20to