ok%20Sabha%20election%20that%20is%20expected%20later%20the%20same%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20big%20names%20absent%20are%20Health%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20(Gujarat)%2C%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20(Madhya%20Pradesh)%2C%20and%20junior%20IT%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar%20(Karnataka).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20absent%20are%20Environment%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20(Rajasthan)%2C%20and%20Fisheries%20Minister%20Parshottam%20Rupala%20(Gujarat)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Micro%2C%20Small%2C%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20Minister%20Narayan%20Rane%20and%20junior%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20represented%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20all%20seven%20could%20now%20be%20fielded%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20in%20various%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20indicate%20Mr%20Pradhan%20may%20be%20fielded%20from%20Sambalpur%20or%20Dheknal%20in%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Odisha%2C%20while%20Mr%20Yadav%20may%20run%20from%20Rajasthan's%20Alwar%20or%20Mahendragarh%2C%20and%20Mr%20Chandrashekhar%20could%20contest%20one%20of%20the%20four%20seats%20in%20Bengaluru%3B%20three%20of%20these%20-%20Central%2C%20North%2C%20and%20South%20-%20are%20held%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Mr%20Mandaviya%20may%20run%20from%20Bhavnagar%20or%20Surat%20in%20Guajrat%2C%20while%20Mr%20Rupala%20may%20get%20Rajkot.%20Mr%20Muraleedharan%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20may%20be%20fielded%20from%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Kerala%3B%20the%20BJP%20has%20no%20presence%20there%2C%20and%20may%20look%20to%20high-profile%20names%20to%20revive%20its%20fortunes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20retained%20only%20a%20few%20big%20names%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20only%20two%20union%20ministers%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20have%20been%20retained%20-%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20(Odisha)%20and%20junior%20Fisheries%20Minister%20L%20Murugan%20(Madhya%20Pradesh).%20No%20outgoing%20MP%20who%20has%20served%20two%20or%20more%20terms%20has%20been%20repeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-fields-jp-nadda-ashok-chavan-for-rajya-sabha-sena-names-milind-deora-5056270%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20Fields%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%20For%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Sena%20Names%20Milind%20Deora%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20exception%20is%20party%20boss%20JP%20Nadda.%20He%20though%2C%20has%20been%20shifted%20-%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20the%20Congress%20won%20in%202022%2C%20to%20Gujarat.%20It%20has%20also%20found%20space%20for%20new%20entrants%2C%20including%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%2C%20who%20quit%20the%20Congress%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20it%20is%20all%20change%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-renominates-only-4-of-28-outgoing-rajya-sabha-mps-5057353%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20four%20of%2028%20outgoing%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20renominated%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0The%20remaining%2024%20have%20reportedly%20been%20asked%20for%20their%20preference%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20named%2028%20candidates%20to%20the%2056%20seats%20that%20will%20fall%20vacant%20in%20April%2C%20with%20the%20focus%20on%20new%20faces%20and%20emphasising%20-%20to%20its%20leadership%20structure%20and%20the%20voters%20-%20its%20determination%20to%20recognise%20grassroots%20workers%2C%20even%20those%20who%20not%20known%20to%20the%20%C2%A0public%2C%20while%20also%20factoring%20in%20social%20equations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20notable%20point%20is%20that%20three%20of%20the%20BJP's%20new%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20-%20Dharmshila%20Gupta%20(Bihar)%2C%20Medha%20Kulkarni%20(Maharashtra)%2C%20and%20Maya%20Naroliya%20(Madhya%20Pradesh)%20-%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20women's%20wing%2C%20