her-rizta-electric-scooter-what-we-know-so-far%2Farticleshow%2F107710964.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Unconstitutional'%3A%20SC%20Strikes%20Down%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Scheme%2C%20Orders%20Disclosure%20of%20Donation%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15105735%2FUntitled-design-8-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%2C%20February%2015%2C%20struck%20down%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20declaring%20it%20unconstitutional%20and%20saying%20that%20anonymous%20electoral%20bonds%20are%20violative%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1218090%2F%5C%22%3EArticle%2019(1)(a)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20it%20asked%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20furnish%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20the%20details%20of%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20which%20would%20presumably%20include%20donors%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20details%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20which%20received%20the%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20publish%20these%20details%20on%20the%20website%20by%20March%2013%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20has%20also%20stopped%20the%20issue%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20was%20brought%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20early%20in%202018.%20Through%20it%2C%20companies%20and%20individuals%20in%20India%20can%20make%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reporter%20Arvind%20Gunasekar%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farvindgunasekar%2Fstatus%2F1758007234389545392%5C%22%3Eordered%3C%2Fa%3E%20political%20parties%20to%20refund%20un-encashed%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20donor%20individuals%20and%20companies%20if%20they%20are%20within%20the%2015-day%20validity%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20the%20court%20arrived%20at%20a%C2%A0unanimous%20decision%20with%20two%20opinions%2C%20one%20by%20the%20CJI%20himself%20and%20another%20by%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20arrive%20at%20same%20conclusion.%20There%20is%20a%20slight%20variance%20in%20the%20reasoning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20live%20posts%20on%20X%20from%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20comprises%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%2C%20and%20Manoj%20Misra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20Companies%20Act%20are%20unconstitutional.%20It%20noted%20that%20the%20infringement%20to%20the%20right%20to%20information%20is%20not%20justified%20with%20the%20stated%20purpose%20of%20curbing%20black%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%2C%20while%20reading%20out%20the%20judgment%2C%20also%20said%20that%20financial%20contributions%20to%20political%20parties%20are%20made%20either%20to%20support%20it%20or%20in%20fulfilment%20of%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20to%20privacy%20of%20political%20affiliation%20does%20not%20extend%20to%20contributions%20made%20to%20influence%20public%20policy%20and%20applies%20only%20to%20contributions%20below%20the%20threshold%2C%C2%A0%20the%20bench%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20while%20the%20ruling%20party%20would%20have%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20donors%2C%20no%20opposition%20party%20could%20have%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20that%20challenged%20the%20scheme%20in%20the%20apex%20court%20are%20Congress%20leader%20Jaya%20Thakur%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20and%20the%20non-governmental%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20arguments%20in%20the%20case%20over%20three%20days%20last%20year.%20On%20November%202%2C%20it%20reserved%20its%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20bonds%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%20570%20crores%20have%20been%20sold%20in%20the%20latest%20phase%20of%20the%20sale%20that%20lasted%20from%20January%202%20to%20January%2011%2C%202024%2C%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-economy%2Felectoral-bonds-worth-more-than-rs-570-crore-sold-in-january-alone-60-in-the-value-of-rs-1-crore%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Equery%20filed%20by%20transparency%20activist%20Commodore%20Lokesh%20Batra%20has%20revealed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fbiz-tech%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2Fsbi-issues-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-16518-crore-in-30-tranches.html%5C%22%3ERs%2016%2C518%20crore%20worth%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20sold%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202018%20to%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20the%20government%20recently%20informed%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707975508000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15105735%2FUntitled-design-8-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20was%20brought%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20early%20in%202018.%20The%20SC%20has%20now%20asked%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20furnish%20the%20details%20of%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20of%20political%20parties%20which%20received%20the%20contributions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delta%20Flight%20Returns%20To%20Amsterdam%20After%20Maggots%20Fall%20On%20Passengers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Delta%20Airlines%20flight%20from%20Europe%20to%20the%20United%20States%20was%20forced%20to%20turn%20around%20after%20maggots%20began%20raining%20on%20to%20plane%20passengers%20from%20an%20overhead%20compartment.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ESkyNews%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Tuesday%20aboard%20a%20flight%20from%20Amsterdam%20to%20Detroit.%20The%20plane%20was%20already%20mid-air%20when%20passengers%20sitting%20in%20the%20economy%20seats%20complained%20about%20the%20insects%20raining%20down%20on%20them%20from%20the%20overhead%20bin.%20It%20later%20emerged%20that%20the%20maggots%20had%20infested%20rotting%20fish%20that%20a%20passenger%20had%20stored%20in%20their%20carry-on%20luggage%2C%20which%20was%20kept%20in%20the%20overhead%20compartment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20forced%20the%20plane%20to%20turn%20around%20an%20hour%20after%20take-off%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmaggots-raining-on-plane-passengers-force-flight-to-make-u-turn-13071584%5C%22%3Eoutlet%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20Once%20it%20landed%2C%20all%20passengers%20were%20instructed%20to%20de-board%20the%20aircraft%20and%20the%20suitcase%20containing%20the%20fish%20was%20placed%20in%20a%20bag%20to%20be%20destroyed.%20The%20plane%20was%20also%20deeply%20cleaned%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Fnews-and-advice%2Fdelta-flight-maggots-passengers-b2496237.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20passenger%20named%20Kelce%20ended%20up%20taking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20to%20share%20her%20experience.%20%26quot%3BReally%20lovely%20to%20be%202%20hours%20into%20an%208%20hour%20%40Delta%20to%20Amsterdam%20and%20find%20out%20there%20is%20rotten%20fish%20and%20maggots%20hitching%20