.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoody's%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20highlighted%20the%20completion%20of%20several%20debt%20transactions%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20including%20refinancing%20and%20obtaining%20new%20loan%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20ensuing%20period%2C%20the%20Group%20has%20completed%20a%20number%20of%20debt%20transactions%2C%20including%20refinancing%20as%20well%20as%20obtaining%20new%20loan%20facilities%2C%20demonstrating%20its%20continued%20access%20to%20debt%20capital%20at%20a%20reasonable%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20noted%20high-profile%20equity%20transactions%20by%20large%20institutional%20and%20strategic%20investors%20such%20as%20GQG%20and%20Qatar%20Investment%20Authority%2C%20showcasing%20the%20Adani%20Group's%20sustained%20access%20to%20the%20equity%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ratings%20of%20the%20four%20companies%20were%20revised%20to%20'negative'%20in%20February%20last%20year%20after%20the%20Adani%20Group%20suffered%20a%20stock%20rout%20sparked%20by%20Hindenburg%20Research's%20market%20manipulation%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20now%20stands%20cleared%20of%20the%20charges%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20saying%20there%20is%20no%20apparent%20regulatory%20failure%20attributable%20to%20markets%20regulator%20SEBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20stated%20that%20the%20conclusion%20of%20most%20regulatory%20investigations%20into%20the%20Adani%20Group%20without%20evidence%20of%20wrongdoing%20has%20reduced%20downside%20risk.%20The%20repayment%20of%20all%20promoter%20loans%20linked%20to%20share%20prices%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20bank%20loans%20raised%20by%20multiple%20group%20entities%20at%20competitive%20rates%20reflects%20restored%20access%20to%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20rating%20affirmations%20and%20upgrades%20underscore%20the%20high%20credit%20quality%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20with%20stable%20and%20predictable%20cash%20flows%20across%20all%20its%20issuers.%20The%20Adani%20Portfolio%20now%20boasts%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20Investment%20Grade%20(BBB-%2FBaa3%20and%20higher)%20rated%20issuances%20among%20private%20companies%20in%20India%2C%20equivalent%20to%20India's%20sovereign%20rating.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707973860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fr5obeg8g_adani-reuters_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fratings-agencies-thumbs-up-to-adani-group-after-robust-performance-5061065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20boost%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20international%20rating%20agencies%20have%20reaffirmed%20and%20upgraded%20the%20credit%20ratings%20for%20companies%20within%20the%20group.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fratings-agencies-thumbs-up-to-adani-group-after-robust-performance-5061065%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fratings-agencies-thumbs-up-to-adani-group-after-robust-performance-5061065%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fratings-agencies-thumbs-up-to-adani-group-after-robust-performance-5061065%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%203%20Of%20Protest%3A%20Rail%20Roko%20Across%20Punjab%2C%20Big%20Centre-Farmer%20Leaders%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20ongoing%20standoff%20between%20protesting%20farmers%20and%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%2C%20a%20panel%20of%20three%20Union%20ministers%20is%20set%20to%20engage%20in%20another%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20farmer%20leaders%20in%20Chandigarh%20today.%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Arjun%20Munda%2C%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20and%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20will%20convene%20at%205%20pm%20to%20address%20the%20farmers'%20various%20demands%2C%20pro