20impact%20of%20tear%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20has%20decided%20to%20hold%20protests%20at%20toll%20plazas%20from%2011%20am%20to%202%20pm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20sealed%20the%20border%20with%20barricades%2C%20preventing%20farmers%20from%20travelling%20to%20Delhi%20on%20their%20tractor-trolleys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20protests%20affecting%20traffic%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%2C%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20last%20night%20issued%20an%20advisory%20urging%20students%20to%20plan%20their%20commute%20early.%20The%20board%20recommended%20using%20the%20metro.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707973740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ft1iplp2o_farmers-protest-_625x300_15_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-3-of-protest-rail-roko-across-punjab-big-centre-farmer-leaders-meet-5061034%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20ongoing%20standoff%20between%20protesting%20farmers%20and%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%2C%20a%20panel%20of%20three%20Union%20ministers%20is%20set%20to%20engage%20in%20another%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20farmer%20leaders%20in%20Chandigarh%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-3-of-protest-rail-roko-across-punjab-big-centre-farmer-leaders-meet-5061034%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-3-of-protest-rail-roko-across-punjab-big-centre-farmer-leaders-meet-5061034%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-3-of-protest-rail-roko-across-punjab-big-centre-farmer-leaders-meet-5061034%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20Modi's%2010%20Years%20Have%20Created%20Fragile%2082%20Crore%20Indians%20on%20Fr