ries%20of%20measures%20to%20prevent%20Hamas%20from%20getting%20access%20to%20its%20satellite%20internet%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20will%20be%20available%20to%20some%20authorities%20in%20Israel%20and%20the%20government%20approved%20it%20for%20use%20at%20a%20field%20hospital%20run%20by%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20in%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Israeli%20communications%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20selling%20terminals%20via%20an%20Israeli%20subsidiary%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20will%20initially%20restrict%20sales%20to%20a%20list%20of%20approved%20clients%20in%20Israel%20that%20include%20local%20councils%20and%20government%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnits%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20to%20support%20humanitarian%20causes%20will%20be%20approved%20individually%2C%20only%20after%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20confirmed%20it%20to%20be%20an%20authorized%20entity%20with%20no%20concern%20of%20risk%20or%20possibility%20of%20endangering%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Communications%20Minister%20Shlomo%20Karhi%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink's%20services%20have%20been%20increasingly%20used%20in%20conflict%20zones%20to%20provide%20internet%20in%20areas%20where%20the%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20destroyed%2C%20including%20to%20military%20units.%20Musk%20activated%20the%20satellite%20service%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20months%20after%20Russia%20invaded.%20The%20Ukrainian%20intelligence%20has%20said%20Russian%20forces%20are%20now%20using%20Starlink%20terminals%20on%20the%20frontline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20will%20use%20the%20service%20for%20emergency%20backup%20communications%2C%20but%20required%20assurances%20from%20its%20parent%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20that%20Hamas%20-%20the%20group%20controlling%20Gaza%20that's%20been%20designated%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20US%20and%20European%20Union%20-%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20access%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20will%20partner%20with%20international%20and%20regional%20organizations%20to%20introduce%20the%20service%20at%20its%20Gaza%20field%20hospital%2C%20a%20spokeswoman%20for%20the%20country's%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20began%20with%20attacks%20on%20Oct.%207%2C%20when%20Palestinian%20militants%20invaded%20southern%20Israel%2C%20killing%20about%201%2C200%20people%20and%20taking%20over%20200%20hostage.%20More%20than%2028%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israel's%20ground%20and%20air%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas%20health%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20been%20eager%20to%20show%20his%20alliance%20with%20Israel%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20visiting%20the%20country%20in%20November%20and%20touring%20some%20of%20the%20massacre%20sites%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20billionaire%20has%20been%20criticized%20for%20amplifying%20antisemitic%20content%20on%20his%20social%20platform%2C%20X%2C%20and%20allowing%20hate%20speech%20to%20flourish%20on%20the%20site%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20our%20hope%20to%20help%20both%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20and%2C%20with%20all%20due%20care%2C%20innocent%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20approval%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsrael%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20greatly%20appreciated.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20such%20a%20terrible%20situation%2C%20we%20should%20strive%20for%20conspicuous%20acts%20of%20kindness%20whenever%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1757813478172340451%3Fref_src%3Dtw