okowis-approval-rating-hits-76-in-lsi-survey%5C%22%3Eapproval%20rating%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20Jokowi%20won%20a%20mayoral%20seat%20in%20Surakarta%20and%20in%202012%20the%20governorship%20of%20Jakarta.%20He%20then%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20as%20president%20challenged%20the%20dominant%20political%20powers%20in%20Jakarta.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F322c7f9b-310a-4c4f-ae6e-598328f59028%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20journalist%20Ben%20Bland%2C%20this%20once-furniture%20maker%20campaigned%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccountry%20with%20faster%20economic%20growth%2C%20lower%20rates%20of%20poverty%2C%20more%20jobs%2C%20less%20corruption%20and%20a%20political%20system%20that%20served%20the%20people%2C%20not%20the%20powerful%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%20focused%20Indonesia%20on%20economic%20development%20and%20corruption-free%20leadership.%20In%20his%202019%20inauguration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F10%2F20%2Fthe-main-thing-is-not-the-process-but-the-result-jokowis-full-inauguration-speech.html%5C%22%3Espeech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20laid%20out%20his%20ambition%20to%20make%20Indonesia%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202045%20and%20one%20of%20the%20top%20five%20world%20economies%20with%20a%20poverty%20rate%20nearing%200%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20five%20key%20pillars%20of%20this%20plan%20%E2%80%93%20economic%20growth%2C%20poverty%20eradication%2C%20anti-corruption%2C%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20and%20infrastructure%20development%20%E2%80%93%20we%20learn%20that%20not%20much%20has%20changed%20in%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20bid%20to%20reform%20the%20political%20system%20has%20also%20fallen%20by%20the%20wayside.%20The%20system%20that%20serves%20the%20people%20now%20also%20serves%20the%20powerful%20more.%20They%20consist%20of%20the%20forces%20of%20conservative%20Islam%2C%20the%20party%20oligarchs%2C%20the%20military%20and%20Jokowi%20himself.%20Over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20Jokowi%20has%20done%20much%20to%20entrench%20himself%20in%20Indonesian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20scoreboard%20remains%20moderate.%20As%20of%202024%2C%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20economy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Farticle%2Fexplainers%2Ftop-10-largest-economies-in-the-world%2F86159%2F1%5C%22%3Eremains%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20sixteenth%20position%2C%20the%20same%20as%20in%202019.%20This%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20other%20economic%20parameters.%20According%20to%20the%20World%20Bank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FSI.POV.NAHC%3Flocations%3DID%26most_recent_year_desc%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20country%20has%20made%20a%20fair%20bit%20of%20progress%20under%20Jokowi%20in%20bringing%20down%20the%20poverty%20rate%20%E2%80%93%20from%20approximately%2011.3%25%20to%209.5%25%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findonesia-elections-what-you-need-to-know%5C%22%3EIndonesia%20Elections%3A%20What%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20numbers%20have%20more%20or%20less%20remained%20static%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20second%20Jokowi%20administration%20%E2%80%93%209.4%25%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trend%20of%20static%20numbers%20is%20mirrored%20in%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20corruption%20perception%20index%20(CPI)%20as%20well.%20Data%20from%20Transparency%20International%20shows%20that%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%202023%20CPI%20score%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transparency.org%2Fen%2Fcpi%2F2023%2Findex%2Fidn%5C%22%3Esimilar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%202014%20score%3A%2034%2F100.%20While%20the%20score%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20its%20ranking%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20has%20fallen%20from%20107%20to%20115%2C%20except%20for%20in%202019%20when%20it%20ranked%2085th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unemployment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceicdata.com%2Fen%2Findicator%2Findonesia%2Funemployment-rate%5C%22%3Erate%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20ranged%20between%205%25%20to%206%25%20from%202014%20to%202023%2C%20except%20for%20a%20rise%20to%207%25%20in%202020%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20all%20the%20parameters%2C%20Indonesia%20under%20Jokowi%20has%20done%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.doingbusiness.org%2Fen%2Fdata%2Fexploreeconomies%2Findonesia%5C%22%3Ebest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%20From%20a%20rank%20of%20120%20in%202014%2C%20Indonesia%20rose%20to%2073rd%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F322c7f9b-310a-4c4f-ae6e-598328f59028%5C%22%3Epositioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cking%20of%20infrastructure%E2%80%9D.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20progress%20on%20several%20big-ticket%20infrastructure%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20Trans-Sumatra%20toll%20road%2C%20the%20Pemalang-Batang%20Toll%20Road%20in%20central%20Java%2C%20the%20Jatigede%20Dam%20in%20west%20Java%20and%20the%20Jakarta%20Mass%20Rapid%20Transit%20(MRT)%20amongst%20others%20have%20allowed%20him%20to%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20numbers%20project%20an%20above-average%20outcome%2C%20they%20have%20been%20enough%20to%20keep%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20political%20manoeuvres%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20the%20political%20arena%20though%2C%20that%20we%20see%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20serious%20successes.%20These%20include%20constitutional%20amendments%2C%20electoral%20manipulations%20and%20political%20manoeuvres%20allowing%20him%20to%20secure%20a%20powerful%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202014%20presidential%20elections%2C%20Jokowi%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fspectre-of-anti-communist-smears-resurrected-against-jokowi-28730%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20being%20from%20a%20secret%20Christian%20Chinese%20community%20with%20communist%20sympathies.%20Given%20the%20historical%20tensions%20between%20the%20Indonesian%20Islamists%20and%20communists%2C%20these%20accusations%20dented%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20ambition.%20This%20motivated%20Jokowi%20to%20co-opt%20Islamic%20hardliner%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20very%20near%20end%20of%20his%20campaign%2C%20Jokowi%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fas-indonesia-vote-nears-a-trip-to-mecca-1404746650%5C%22%3Emade%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20trip%20to%20Mecca.%20Two%20years%20into%20his%20presidency%20in%202016%2C%20Jokowi%20aligned%20himself%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98212%E2%80%99%20movement%20led%20by%20religious%20extremists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjakartaglobe.id%2Fnews%2Funderstanding-212-movement%5C%22%3Eagainst%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20then-governor%20of%20Jakarta%20and%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20close%20ally%2C%20Basuki%20Tjahaja%20Purnama%20(Ahok).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20revolved%20around%20the%20alleged%20blasphemy%20against%20Islam%20by%20Jakarta%E2%80%99s%20Christian%20Chinese%20governor%20Ahok.%20The%20protestors%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmandala.org%2Fjokowi-hands-strategic-victory-radicals%2F%5C%22%3Evalidated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20presence%20on%20stage%20alongside%20the%20extremist%20leaders.%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20concern%20was%20so%20strong%20that%20he%20not%20only%20allowed%20his%20one-time%20ally%20Ahok%20to%20be%20thrown%20under%20the%20bus%2C%20but%20he%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F2018-08-09%2Findonesia-s-jokowi-picks-muslim-cleric-in-bid-for-second-term%5C%22%3Epartnered%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Ma%E2%80%99ruf%20Amin%2C%20the%20ex-head%20of%20Nahdlatul%20Ulama%2C%20who%20became%20his%20vice-presidential%20candidate%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20push%20for%20the%20military%20to%20re-enter%20Indonesian%20politics%20and%20business%20has%20also%20turned%20the%20political%20tables%20in%20Jakarta.%20Their%20re-entry%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Fgenerals-gaining-ground-civil-military-relations-and-democracy-in-indonesia%2F%5C%22%3Eignited%3C%2Fa%3E%20conversations%20on%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20Suharto-era%20doctrine%20of%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Edwi%20fungsi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(or%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdual%20function%E2%80%9D)%20which%20ended%20in%201998.%C2%A0%20Under%20Jokowi%2C%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20dual%20role%20became%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thejakartapost.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F09%2F20%2Findonesian-military-deployed-for-coronavirus-fight.html%5C%22%3Eapparent%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20the%20military%20was%20deployed%20to%20enforce%20health%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20has%20also%20witnessed%20the%20appointment%20of%20military%20officials%20to%20political%20committees%20and%20their%20inclusion%20in%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20inner%20circle.%20Some%20powerful%20military%20appointees%20include%20minister%20of%20maritime%20affairs%20and%20investments%20Luhut%20Pandjaitan%2C%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20chief%20of%20staff%20Moeldoko%20and%20defence%20minister%20Prabowo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F10%2F23%2Findonesias-widodo-appoints-archrival-as-defence-minister%5C%22%3Einclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20is%20the%20most%20intriguing%20of%20them%20all.%20Peace%20with%20Prabowo%2C%20dictator%20Suharto%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%20and%20a%20general%20with%20countless%20human%20rights%20abuses%20to%20his%20name%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20glar