E%20with%20the%20212%20movement%20to%20oppose%20Jokowi%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%20was%20dismissed%20from%20his%20military%20duties%20after%20the%201998%20Indonesian%20riots%20and%20was%20denied%20a%20US%20visa%20for%20almost%2020%20years.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20succeeded%20in%20perhaps%20his%20last%20attempt%20at%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20alongside%20Prabowo%20as%20the%20vice%20president-elect%20is%20none%20other%20than%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20son%2C%20Gibran%20Rakabuming%20Raka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaka%2C%2036%2C%20is%20the%20incumbent%20mayor%20of%20Surakarta%2C%20a%20seat%20that%20his%20father%20once%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20not%2C%20however%2C%20eligible%20to%20run%20for%20these%20elections%20owing%20to%20the%20minimum%20age%20criteria%20of%2040%20years.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbcindonesia.com%2Fresearch%2F20231017064610-128-481086%2Fputusan-mk-gibran-12-kepala-daerah-ini-bisa-maju-cawapres%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%20of%20Indonesia%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20brother-in-law%20Anwar%20Usman%20allowed%20%E2%80%9Csomeone%20who%20is%20not%20yet%2040%20years%20old%20to%20run%20for%20president%20or%20vice%20president%20as%20long%20as%20they%20have%20experience%20as%20a%20regional%20head%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20a%20major%20uproar%20across%20Indonesia%2C%20but%20helped%20secure%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Jokowi%20leaves%20behind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJokowi%E2%80%99s%20transformation%20from%20a%20rank%20outsider%20to%20a%20consummate%20insider%20has%20reached%20its%20final%20lap.%20His%20original%20raison%20d%E2%80%99%C3%AAtre%20started%20to%20peel%20away%20as%20he%20built%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Findonesias-new-cabinet-built-on-political-transactions-631