3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESalih%20outlined%20how%20Iraqi%20Kurds%20perceive%20themselves%20%E2%80%9Cconsistently%20targeted%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20their%20association%20with%20the%20US%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20merely%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20they%20resisted%20political%20efforts%20by%20pro-Iran%20groups%20to%20expel%20US%20troops%20from%20Iraq.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIraqi%20Kurdistan%20expects%20the%20US%20to%20appreciate%20such%20stances%20and%20provide%20air%20defenses%2C%20given%20the%20high%20stakes%20for%20the%20autonomous%20region.%20That%20could%20either%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20US%20supplying%20such%20weaponry%20directly%20to%20the%20Peshmerga%20or%20having%20the%20US%20military%20expand%20its%20limited%20air%20defense%20capabilities%20in%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%20to%20cover%20the%20region%20rather%20than%20just%20US%20bases%20and%20the%20American%20consulate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECeng%20Sagnic%2C%20chief%20of%20analysis%20of%20the%20geopolitical%20consultancy%20firm%20TAM-C%20Solutions%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20considerations%E2%80%9D%20are%20involved%20in%20supplying%20the%20Peshmerga%20air%20defenses.%20In%20his%20view%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprimary%20concern%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20requirement%20under%20the%20current%20NDAA%20also%20to%20arm%20the%20Iraqi%20military%20with%20such%20systems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20US%20might%20hesitate%20to%20provide%20advanced%20weaponry%20to%20the%20central%20Iraqi%20government%2C%20especially%20given%20Baghdad%E2%80%99s%20inclination%20to%20formally%20request%20the%20departure%20of%20coalition%20forces%20from%20Iraq%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagnic%20told%20Insider.%20%E2%80%9CConsequently%2C%20the%20central%20Iraqi%20government%20might%20delay%20acquiring%20air%20defense%20systems%20from%20the%20US%20to%20prevent%20their%20delivery%20to%20the%20Kurdish%20region%20on%20guidance%20from%20Iran.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThreat%20perceptions%20in%20Baghdad%20and%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%E2%80%99s%20Erbil%20also%20differ%20since%20the%20former%20has%20not%20come%20under%20aerial%20threat%20from%20Iran%20or%20its%20proxies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%20to%20receive%20advanced%20weapon%20systems%20from%20the%20US%2C%20a%20decision%20circumventing%20the%20central%20Iraqi%20government%20is%20necessary%2C%20as%20has%20occurred%20in%20the%20past%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20war%20against%20ISIS%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagnic%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETurkey%20may%20not%20object%20to%20an%20American%20air%20defense%20provision%20to%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%20under%20certain%20conditions.%20While%20Ankara%20has%20friendly%20ties%20with%20the%20leading%20Kurdistan%20Democratic%20Party%20in%20Erbil%2C%20it%20objects%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20second%20party%2C%20the%20Patriotic%20Union%20of%20Kurdistan%2C%20repeatedly%20accusing%20it%20of%20collaborating%20with%20its%20arch-foe%2C%20the%20Kurdistan%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Party%2C%20PKK.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20unlikely%20that%20Ankara%20would%20oppose%20arming%20Iraqi%20Kurdish%20forces%20with%20air%20defense%20weapons%2C%20as%20they%20would%20ultimately%20serve%20to%20protect%20Turkish%20interests%20against%20potential%20Iranian%20aggressions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagnic%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20Ankara%20will%20closely%20monitor%20the%20recipients%20of%20these%20shipments%20if%20the%20US%20provides%20such%20weapons%20to%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%2C%20aiming%20to%20prevent%20PKK-allied%20PUK%20from%20acquiring%20advanced%20weaponry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Syrian%20Democratic%20Forces%20and%20the%20north%20and%20eastern%20Syrian%20regions%20under%20its%20control%20have%20come%20under%20unprecedented%20aerial%20attacks%20in%20recent%20months.%20Turkey%20has%20bombarded%20the%20region%20in%20a%20ferocious%20campaign%20of%20air%20and%20drone%20strikes.%20And%20Iran-backed%20militias%20have%20also%20targeted%20the%20SDF%20with%20drones.%20On%20Feb.%205%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fsyria-iraq-sdf-islamic-resistance-us-c621972db21d6b3db7ca1bccd50ce6ef%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Esix%20SDF%20fighters%20were%20killed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20when%20an%20explosive%20drone%20launched%20by%20an%20Iran-backed%20militia%20hit%20their%20base%2C%20which%20also%20houses%20US%20troops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMazlum%20Kobane%2C%20the%20SDF%E2%80%99s%20commander%20in%20chief%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-backed-force-syria-more-air-defence-needed-after-deadly-drone-attack-2024-02-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20Reuters%20on%20Feb.%208%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20his%20forces%20%E2%80%9Crequire%20technical%20capabilities%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20aerial%20defensive%20systems%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20900%20US%20troops%20in%20Syria%20have%20some%20limited%20defenses%2C%20including%20short-range%20Avenger%20systems%20that%20fire%20Stinger%20missiles.%20These%20defenses%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Fus-led-coalition-blocks-attacks-at-conoco-oil-field-in-syria-%2F7482765.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Eintercepted%20six%20incoming%20militia%20drones%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Feb.%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20US%20provision%20of%20such%20systems%20to%20the%20SDF%20would%20likely%20face%20opposition%20from%20Turkey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20recent%20clashes%20as%20a%20reason%20to%20request%20additional%20US%20air%20defenses%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20viewed%20negatively%20in%20Ankara%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ali%20Bakir%2C%20a%20Turkey%20expert%20and%20non-resident%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Atlantic%20Council%E2%80%99s%20Middle%20East%20program%2C%20told%20BI.%20%E2%80%9CDepending%20on%20the%20type%20and%20location%20of%20the%20air%20defense%20system%2C%20it%20could%20be%20perceived%20as%20a%20threat%20against%20Turkey%20rather%20than%20protection%20against%20Iran.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20these%20numerous%20obstacles%2C%20a%20workable%20solution%20that%20gives%20the%20Kurds%20some%20defense%20against%20aerial%20threats%20might%20still%20be%20found.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20Iraqi%20Kurdistan%20may%20eventually%20secure%20advanced%20mid-range%20missile%20systems%20for%20defensive%20purposes%2C%20the%20optimal%20choice%20for%20the%20SDF%20might%20involve%20requesting%20that%20the%20US%20military%20safeguard%20SDF-controlled%20areas%20using%20weaponry%20operated%20by%20US%20personnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagnic%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-kurds-middle-east-demand-air-defenses-iranian-drone-attacks-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707949861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd1b6f6fcb546d2d4fd856%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-kurds-middle-east-demand-air-defenses-iranian-drone-attacks-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iraqi%20Kurds%20are%20facing%20Iranian%20drone%20attacks%20and%20believe%20they're%20being%20targeted%20because%20of%20their%20support%20for%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Paul%20Iddon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-kurds-middle-east-demand-air-defenses-iranian-drone-attacks-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suddenly%2C%20there's%20re