r%20drug%20trafficking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707937020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-quincy-promes-netherlands_6455739.jpg%3F20240214195537%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fquincy-promes-former-dutch-international-footballer-sentenced-to-six-years-in-prison-for-drug-trafficking-13071736%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Dutch%20international%20footballer%20and%20once%20a%20target%20of%20Manchester%20United%2C%20Quincy%20Promes%2C%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20six%20years%20in%20prison%20in%20absentia%20for%20drug%20trafficking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fquincy-promes-former-dutch-international-footballer-sentenced-to-six-years-in-prison-for-drug-trafficking-13071736%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fquincy-promes-former-dutch-international-footballer-sentenced-to-six-years-in-prison-for-drug-trafficking-13071736%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fquincy-promes-former-dutch-international-footballer-sentenced-to-six-years-in-prison-for-drug-trafficking-13071736%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Inaugurates%20Hindu%20Temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15000032%2FModi%2540BAPS-2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%20inaugurated%20a%20Rs%20700%20crore%20Hindu%20temple%20with%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaarti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE).%20The%20temple%20was%20built%20over%20four%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20is%20currently%20on%20his%20seventh%20visit%20to%20the%20Gulf%20emirate%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20making%20the%20UAE%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20second-most%20frequently%20visited%20foreign%20nation%20along%20with%20France%20and%20Japan%2C%20behind%20only%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20his%20second%20day%2C%20Modi%20spoke%20at%20the%20World%20Government%20Summit%2C%20but%20the%20media%20hype%20over%20this%20UAE%20visit%20was%20over%20the%20Hindu%20temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UAE%20has%20had%20several%20Hindu%20temples%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20this%20temple%20run%20by%20a%20Gujarat-based%20Hindu%20denomination%20has%20been%20described%20as%20the%20first%20one%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Abu%20Dhabi%20and%20the%20first%20such%20stone%20temple%20in%20the%20Gulf%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20inauguration%2C%20Modi%20sought%20to%20draw%20parallels%20with%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20strategy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20joy%20we%20felt%20in%20Ayodhya%20has%20been%20amplified%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20today.%20It%20is%20my%20honour%20that%20I%20witnessed%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20last%20month%20and%20this%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20built%20following%20a%20judgement%20of%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202019%2C%20three%20decades%20after%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20at%20the%20very%20same%20spot%20by%20a%20crowd%20of%20Hindutva%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20operated%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBAPS%20Swaminarayan%20Sanstha%2C%20is%20spread%20over%2027%20acres%20and%20has%20been%20constructed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20over%20Rs%20700%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20temple%20in%20the%20UAE%20was%20opened%20in%201958%20in%20Bur%20Dubai.%20It%20was%20relocated%20this%20year%20to%20Jebel%20Ali%2C%20but%20the%20closure%20of%20the%2066-year-old%20temple%20had%20led%20to%20mixed%20emotions%20among%20its%20loyal%20congregation%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenationalnews.com%2Fuae%2F2024%2F01%2F03%2Fworshippers-heartbroken-as-bur-dubai-hindu-temple-closes%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20newspaper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20UAE%20has%2C%20in%20history%2C%20written%20a%20new%20chapter%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20community%20hall.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20also%20denied%20that%20he%20can%20be%20called%20a%20priest%2C%20which%20he%20is%20described%20as%20by%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20centuries-old%20dream%20was%20fulfilled.%20All%20of%20India%20and%20every%20Indian%20is%20still%20cherishing%20that%20feeling.%20My%20friend%20Brahmavihari%20Swamy%20was%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eji%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20the%20biggest%20priest%E2%80%99.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20I%20have%20the%20qualifications%20of%20a%20temple%20priest%2C%20but%20I%20am%20proud%20to%20be%20a%20priest%20of%20Mother%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Modi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements-hi.htm%3Fdtl%2F37624%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espoke%20at%20the%20World%20Governments%20Summit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cs