p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20have%20become%20an%20opportunity%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20accommodate%20leaders%20in%20parliament%20well%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20new%20faces%20and%20some%20others%20are%20old%2C%20while%20some%20were%20rewarded%20for%20their%20significant%20organisational%20roles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20nominated%20multiple%20leaders%20from%20the%20Sangh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparivar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20while%20regional%20parties%20rewarded%20some%20of%20their%20young%20faces%20who%20have%20remained%20loyal%20despite%20facing%20electoral%20losses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20in%20the%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20that%20the%20BJP%20released%2C%20nine%20Union%20ministers%20whose%20terms%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20were%20ending%20this%20April%20were%20absent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEducation%20minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%2C%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20minister%20Narayan%20Rane%20and%20others%20like%20L.%20Murugan%20and%20Purushottam%20Rupala%20were%20missing%20from%20the%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Murugan%20was%20nominated%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%2C%20while%20railways%2C%20communications%20and%20IT%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20filed%20his%20nomination%20from%20Odisha%20after%20the%20ruling%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20decided%20to%20support%20him%20again%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJunior%20IT%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20was%20not%20re-nominated%20from%20his%20Karnataka%20seat%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20instead%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fnarayansa-bandage-gets-bjp-ticket-for-rs-polls%2Farticle67835920.ece%5C%22%3Echoosing%20to%20field%20the%20Hindutva%20leader%20Narayana%20Bhandage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeculation%20is%20rife%20that%20most%20of%20the%20Union%20ministers%20who%20have%20not%20been%20re-nominated%20for%20the%20elections%20will%20now%20be%20fielded%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20whose%20term%20also%20ends%20in%20April%2C%20was%20re-nominated%20not%20from%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20from%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBarring%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20none%20of%20the%20nine%20outgoing%20BJP%20MPs%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20vacancies%20at%20ten%20seats%2C%20was%20renominated%2C%20which%20means%20leaders%20like%20Anil%20Jain%2C%20Anil%20Agarwal%20and%20G.V.L.%20Narsimha%20Rao%20will%20be%20given%20other%20roles%2C%20mostly%20in%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20accommodated%20former%20Congress%20leader%20R.P.N.%20Singh%2C%20another%20turncoat%20who%20switched%20camps%20in%202022%2C%20from%20its%20UP%20tally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20leaders%20were%20also%20nominated%20as%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rainbow%20social%20representation%20formula%20%E2%80%93%20Chaudhary%20Tejveer%20Singh%2C%20Sadhna%20Singh%2C%20Amarpal%20Maurya%2C%20Sangeeta%20Balwant%20and%20Naveen%20Jain%20are%20some%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20will%20be%20representing%20UP%20for%20their%20party%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20renominated%20actress-politician%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20fielded%20new%20faces%20like%20former%20bureaucrat-turned-party%20advisor%20Alok%20Ranjan%20and%20party%20leader%20and%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman%20as%20its%20choices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nomination%20of%20Bachchan%20and%20Ranjan%20has%20ruffled%20many%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20like%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%20and%20Pallavi%20Patel%2C%20who%20believe%20that%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20should%20have%20been%20used%20to%20nominate%20leaders%20from%20backward%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20eastern%20India%2C%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20three%20seats%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20filled%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJD%E2%80%99s%20Debashish%20Samantray%2C%20a%20senior%20BJD%20leader%20who%20lost%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls%20but%20remained%20loyal%20to%20the%20party%20leadership%3B%20and%20young%20turk%20Subhasish%20Khuntia%20from%20Puri.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20third%20seat%20from%20the%20state%2C%20the%20BJD%20has%20extended%20its%20support%20to%20Vaishnaw%2C%20during%20whose%20tenure%20as%20Union%20railways%20minister%20the%20state%20received%20its%20highest-ever%20investment%20in%20rail%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-kumar-resigns-as-bihar-cm-expected-to-stake-claim-again-in-alliance-with-bjp%5C%22%3Ewhich%20recently%20joined%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%20(NDA)%2C%20has%20nominated%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20close%20aide%2C%20Sanjay%20Jha%2C%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20He%20will%20most%20likely%20win%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20has%20not%20been%20re-nominated%20and%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20he%20will%20be%20fielded%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%20six%20vacant%20seats%20from%20Bihar%2C%20three%20each%20are%20held%20by%20the%20NDA%20and%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFifty-six%20seats%20spread%20across%2015%20states%20will%20be%20filled%20up%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20February%2027.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20retiring%20are%2028%20MPs%20from%20the%20BJP%3B%2011%20from%20the%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%3B%20four%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%3B%20two%20each%20from%20the%20BJD%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%3B%20and%20one%20each%20from%20the%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707914743000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12132623%2FGFuyS5gaQAA6Ifj-1-e1707724634678.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-ashok-chavan-rajya-sabha-milind-deora-shiv-sena-shinde%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20defector%2C%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20has%20been%20nominated%20by%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde).%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20president%2C%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20a%20Gujarat%20MP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-ashok-chavan-rajya-sabha-milind-deora-shiv-sena-shinde%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22200%20Million%20Voters%20and%20820%2C000%20Polling%20Stations%3A%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20Massive%20Election%20in%26nbsp%3BNumbers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14170740%2F45132822702_4e6e0154e4_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndonesians%20are%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20president%20on%20Wednesday.%20There%20are%20three%20candidates%20running%2C%20alongside%20their%20vice%20presidential%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20opinion%20polls%2C%20the%20favourite%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fcute-grandpa-or-authoritarian-in-waiting-who-is-prabowo-subianto-the-favourite-to-win-indonesias-presidential-election-221858%5C%22%3EPrabowo%20Subianto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Greater%20Indonesia%20Party%20(Gerindra)%2C%20a%20populist%20and%20nationalist%20party%20he%20founded%20in%202008.%20A%20former%20army%20general%2C%20Prabowo%20has%20already%20stood%20unsuccessfully%20for%20president%20twice%20before.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20defence%20minister%20in%20the%20cabinet%20of%20the%20current%20president%2C%20Joko%20%E2%80%9CJokowi%E2%80%9D%20Widodo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20contenders%20are%20Ganjar%20Pranowo%2C%20a%20former%20governor%20of%20the%20large%20province%20of%20Central%20Java%20and%20a%20member%20of%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20party%2C%20the%20Indonesian%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20Struggle%20(PDI-P)%2C%20and%20Anies%20Basweden%2C%20an%20independent%20candidate%20who%20was%20governor%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Jakarta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabowo%20is%20the%20frontrunner%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20unclear%20whether%20he%20will%20win%20an%20absolute%20majority%20of%20votes%20in%20the%20first%20round.%20If%20he%20fails%20to%20win%2050.1%25%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20runoff%20election%20between%20the%20two%20leading%20candidates%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F575146%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240212-26-xlmztf.png%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26q%3D45%26auto%3Dformat%26w%3D1000%26fit%3Dclip%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(min-width%3A%201466px)%20754px%2C%20(max-width%3A%20599px)%20100vw%2C%20(min-width%3A%20600px)%20600px%2C%20237px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F575146%2Foriginal%2