2%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F575151%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240212-18-j0czv9.png%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D15%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D576%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D3%201800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F575151%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240212-18-j0czv9.png%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D45%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D724%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D1%20754w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F575151%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240212-18-j0czv9.png%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D30%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D724%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D2%201508w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F575151%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240212-18-j0czv9.png%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D15%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D724%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D3%202262w%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%2C%20KPU%2C%20Perludem%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELogistical%20nightmare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third-largest%20democracy%20after%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%93%20and%20all%20three%20are%20holding%20elections%20this%20year.%20But%20since%20Indonesia%20is%20holding%20five%20separate%20polls%20on%20one%20day%2C%20it%20is%20often%20touted%20as%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20complex%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Findonesia-will-hold-the-worlds-biggest-single-day-election-here-is-what-you-need-to-know-208673%5C%22%3Esingle-day%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20is%20an%20archipelago%20with%20about%206%2C000%20inhabited%20islands%2C%20some%20of%20them%20remote%20and%20with%20limited%20infrastructure.%20The%20distance%20from%20Aceh%20in%20the%20west%20to%20Papua%20in%20the%20east%20is%20some%205%2C100%20kilometres%20(3%2C200%20miles)%2C%20wider%20than%20the%20continental%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20massive%20undertaking%20to%20organise%20an%20election%20of%20this%20size%2C%20from%20procuring%20polling%20station%20equipment%20to%20managing%20a%20huge%20election%20staff%20to%20ensuring%20the%20public%20trusts%20the%20integrity%20and%20fairness%20of%20the%20vote.%20The%20election%20commission%20does%20a%20remarkable%20job%20making%20sure%20the%20vote%20happens%20on%20time%20and%20the%20ballot%20counting%20occurs%20quickly%20and%20without%20tampering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20size%20of%20the%20task%20facing%20the%20KPU%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20the%20presidential%20election%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20204%20million%20registered%20voters%20in%20Indonesia%2C%20so%20the%20KPU%20has%20to%20print%20and%20distribute%20this%20many%20ballots%20across%20the%20country%20for%20the%20presidential%20vote%20alone%2C%20with%20a%20few%20million%20extra%20in%20case%20polling%20stations%20run%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20is%20then%20required%20to%20deliver%2C%20count%20and%20return%20the%20ballots%20to%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifes.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-02%2F2024_Elections_FAQ_Final.pdf%5C%22%3E820%2C000%20domestic%20polling%20stations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20more%20than%203%2C000%20stations%20overseas.%20Since%20there%20may%20be%20a%20second-round%2C%20runoff%20election%2C%20the%20KPU%20must%20be%20ready%20to%20repeat%20the%20whole%20exercise%20in%20a%20few%20months.%20This%20time%20it%20would%20need%20a%20different%20set%20of%20ballot%20papers%20showing%20the%20two%20final%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20get%20really%20complicated%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20contests%20for%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20various%20national%20and%20regional%20parliaments%2C%20even%20though%20these%20get%20relatively%20little%20attention%20compared%20to%20the%20presidential%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presidential%20election%20involves%20a%20simple%20majority%20count%20of%20three%20candidates.%20But%20the%20national%20and%20regional%20parliaments%20are%20conducted%20through%20a%20proportional%20representation%20system%2C%20the%20same%20used%20in%20countries%20like%20Germany%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20for%20the%20Australian%20Senate.%20Under%20this%20system%2C%20parties%20win%20seats%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20votes%20they%20receive.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20party%20winning%2020%25%20of%20the%20votes%20will%20take%20up%20around%2020%25%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20the%20chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20complexity%2C%20voters%20in%20Indonesia%20are%20not%20compelled%20to%20vote%20just%20for%20a%20party%2C%20but%20can%20choose%20an%20individual%20candidate%20within%20a%20party%E2%80%99s%20list.%20So%2C%20when%20voters%20arrive%20at%20the%20polling%20station%2C%20they%20are%20presented%20with%20a%20huge%20ballot%20paper%20for%20the%20national%20parliament%20alone%2C%20which%20lists%2C%20on%20average%2C%20118%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20must%20also%20make%20choices%20for%20three%20other%20chambers%20%E2%80%93%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20presidential%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FDPv5y%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FZSWFJ%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400px%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20unglamorous%2C%20but%20remarkable%20democratic%20achievement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20well%20has%20Indonesia%20done%20in%20this%20massive%20task%20of%20making%20democratic%20elections%20work%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20languishing%20under%20a%20dictatorship%20and%20rigged%20elections%20for%20four%20decades%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20Soeharto%2C%20the%20country%20has%20done%20remarkably%20well%20since%20embracing%20democracy%20in%20the%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Indonesia%20rarely%20receives%20recognition%20for%20this%20transformation.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20democracy%20seems%20increasingly%20under%20pressure%2C%20Indonesia%20has%20managed%20five%20peaceful%20and%20democratic%20transfers%20of%20power.%20In%20comparison%20to%20neighbouring%20states%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmandala.org%2Fcivil-society-and-southeast-asias-authoritarian-turn%2F%5C%22%3Eone-party%20dominance%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20widespread%20or%20democratic%20progress%20has%20been%20crushed%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Fmyanmar-history-coup-military-rule-ethnic-conflict-rohingya%5C%22%3Emilitary%20coups%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Indonesia%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20bastion%20of%20democratic%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20this%20is%20to%20say%20that%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20system%20is%20flawless.%20In%20fact%2C%20domestic%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F00074918.2018.1549918%3Fcasa_token%3DUxIulMCigoYAAAAA%3A6CZA0rTwlhWHlfUU6Y_sxAW1P3-ClmyKNUOlPfArJjAjAddU4jwBgltG41xOeLBi44jbLeISJ6m46B4%5C%22%3Einternational%20observers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20increasingly%20noted%20the%20reemergence%20of%20authoritarian%20instincts%20among%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fasia%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fjokowi-is-building-a-political-dynasty%5C%22%3Edynastic%20politics%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20incumbents%20engineer%20the%20elections%20of%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20not%20only%20applies%20to%20prominent%20figures%20from%20the%20Soeharto%20days%2C%20such%20as%20the%20leading%20presidential%20contender%20Prabowo.%20Jokowi%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fis-joko-widodo-paving-the-way-for-a-political-dynasty-in-indonesia-219499%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20political%20dynasty%20by%20using%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20candidacy%20to%20ensure%20he%E2%80%99ll%20have%20influence%20in%20a%20Prabowo%20presidential%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20electoral%20contest%20itself%2C%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20election%20commission%2C%20while%20not%20perfect%2C%20has%20delivered%20reliable%20and%20trustworthy%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20is%20an%20unglamorous%20job%2C%20but%20it%20is%20crucial%20for%20maintaining%20public%20trust%20in%20the%20political%20system.%20It%20also%20ensures%20that%20candidates%20and%20parties%20accept%20the%20results%20and%20are%20not%20tempted%20to%20launch%20coups%20or%20deliberately%20obstruct%20the%20post-election%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20strains%20placed%20on%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20long-established%20democracy%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20achievement%20in%20making%20elections%20work%20should%20not%20go%20unnoticed.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F222604%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fstephen-sherlock-1508422%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EStephen%20Sherlock%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20Visiting%20Fellow%2C%20Department%20of%20Political%20and%20Social%20Change%2C%20Coral%20Bell%20School%20of%20Asia%20Pacific%20Affairs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Faustralian-national-university-877%5C%22%3EAustralian%20National%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3